"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-news-world-charles-de-gaulle-airport-paris-olympics-bus-fire-b1174067.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"News|World  A thick plume of smoke has been spotted atParis'sCharles De Gaulleairport as thousands visitFrancefor the Olympics.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pictures of the black pillar of smoke were seen rising from near terminal 2F at the major airport amid reports of a bus fire.\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 483, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The blaze appeared to be in the airport, which is one of Europe's busiest.\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The fire engulfed a bus on nearby Rue de New York, according to local reports.\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 602, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999899550059325, \"rank\": 8.992309687693786e-06, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flight services at the terminal were thought to be unaffected.\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 702, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"France's BFMTV reported firefighters intervened with two hoses and managed to bring the fire under control around 4pm local time.\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 704, \"end\": 710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9996927477070725, \"rank\": 0.00024648774373246574, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 713, \"end\": 718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BFMTV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A spokesperson told one concerned passenger on social media: \\\"A bus caught fire in the public area of the airport.\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 949, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The fire fighters intervened and the fire is now fully extinguished.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The passengers have been taken to safety and there are no injuries.\\\"\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1089, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hundreds of thousands of people have descended upon the French capital to watch the games.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1147, \"end\": 1153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8945181387094965, \"rank\": 0.1136540210913768, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In June, firefighters were called to the airport after a Tug master caught fire while towing a Boeing 777.\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1278, \"end\": 1288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boeing_777\", \"score\": 0.999999999834472, \"rank\": 1.6552909090644964e-10, \"text\": \"Boeing 777\", \"types\": [\"Q11436\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boeing_777\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boeing_777\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nobody was injured in that incident.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Last week, in a separate incident,an arson attack hit the nation's high-speed rail network.\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1420, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fires were started at key points just hours before the Olympic opening ceremony, bringing trains to a halt and leading to the cancellation of services taking tens of thousands of spectators to the capital.\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1627, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Transport minister Patrice Vergriete said the \\\"co-ordinated malicious acts\\\" had targeted the TGV network, which spans the country.\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1722, \"end\": 1725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"TGV\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TGV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It meant some Eurostar services between London and Paris were cancelled and others delayed as trains were switched to conventional tracks rather than the 186mph high-speed network.\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1775, \"end\": 1783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 0.9999967044340982, \"rank\": 3.2955766558423077e-06, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}, {\"begin\": 1801, \"end\": 1807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999856659034844, \"rank\": 9.539645322400583e-06,